CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Skycorp Solar Group Limited is a solar PV product provider principally engaged in the manufacture and sale of solar cables and solar connectors. We also actively cultivate partnerships with multiple Integrated Circuit chip manufacturers and offer customers new and used GPU and HPC servers. Our business is carried out through our operating subsidiaries, Ningbo Skycorp and its subsidiaries, in China.
